      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-39vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on Red Hat Enterprise Linux Server 7.3/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/74bd52cc-bd27-11e6-a239-5254006e85c2). Ran 7 tests. No failures.",
