        "subject": "LU-8916 osd-zfs: Correct ZAP size accounting",
        "message": "LU-8916 osd-zfs: Correct ZAP size accounting\n\nThe osd-zfs module does not correctly adjust ZAP\nsizes when inserting and deleting objects. Add\nlogic to properly adjust sizes when entries are\nadded and removed from ZAPs.\n\nSigned-off-by: Giuseppe Di Natale <dinatale2@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I69310420feae99df9e0d8db4f3ba85475b642d4e\n"
